Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.21,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:10.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:20.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.63,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:30.37,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.44,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.77,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:43.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.57,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.51,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.40,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.94,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:16.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:24.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有盡頭的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:02.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不見的羽翼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遙遠的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:10.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不見的未來依舊在等待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:20.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不願清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:23.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:30.37,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包圍 誰也逃不出這個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:33.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:36.77,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變幻不定的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:38.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:43.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.57,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:52.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方聽聞的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震動鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.40,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:07.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我漸漸清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:10.94,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:16.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏不斷變化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:20.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的傷口 是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.38,0:02:24.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因為你和Burst The Gravity
